uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.editors.mail

Interface MessageHandlerFactoryCreator<P extends MessageHandlerFactory>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - type of MessageHandlerFactory

    public interface MessageHandlerFactoryCreator<P extends MessageHandlerFactory>
    Interface for classes that can generate a MessageHandlerFactory. This is intended for cases where a single class can create several different types of message. The MessageHandlerFactory is parameterised by the target factory so we use a 2 step creation process.
